---
title: Seared Beef Rump & Root Veggie Toss with Baby Leaves & Garlic Aioli
description: A crispy stack of colourful roasted veggies creates the base for a steak dish of joyous proportions. Tender slices of beef
rump are seasoned and topped with a garlicky aioli to take things up a notch. Now, if that doesn't sound like heaven
on earth, we don't know what does!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
